<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shrug-v">shrug <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ʃrʌɡ/    美 /ʃrʌɡ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (为表示冷漠、无奈、蔑视、不满等) 耸 (肩)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I just shrugged my shoulders and ignored him.
我只是耸耸肩，不去理睬他。</p></div></div>